OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1778339461
OL,3,CReform UK Leader in Wales Dan Thomas
OL,4,Cwins seat at Senedd Election
OL,6,FDan Thomas the leader of Reform UK in
OL,7,FWales has won his seat in the
OL,8,Fconstituency Casnewydd Islwyn in the
OL,9,FSenedd Election.
OL,11,FIt is the first time Mr Thomas has
OL,12,Fstood to be a Member of the Senedd
OL,13,Fafter being announced the Welsh leader
OL,14,Fof the party in February.
OL,16,FHe was previously a Conservative Party
OL,17,Fcouncillor in the London Borough of
OL,18,FBarnet for more than 19 years from
OL,19,F2006 to 2025.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
