OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1778339461
OL,3,CReform UK Leader in Wales Dan Thomas
OL,4,Cwins seat at Senedd Election
OL,6,FIn Casnewydd Islwyn Reform UK won two
OL,7,Fseats, Plaid Cymru won two seats,
OL,8,FWelsh Labour won one seat, as did the
OL,9,FWelsh Conservatives.
OL,11,FReform UK received a total of 25,571
OL,12,Fvotes in the constituency, over 2,000
OL,13,Fmore than it's nearest opposition
OL,14,FPlaid Cymru who secured 23,069.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
