PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1778339461
OL,3,CReform UK Leader in Wales Dan Thomas
OL,4,Cwins seat at Senedd Election
OL,6,FIn his speech following winning a seat
OL,7,Fin the constituency, Dan Thomas said:
OL,8,F"In just five years reform has gone
OL,9,Ffrom winning 1% of the vote in the
OL,10,FSenedd Elections to now being the main
OL,11,Fcontenders for government - smashing
OL,12,FLabour in the process.
OL,14,F"It has taken Plaid Cymru decades to
OL,15,Fcome anywhere near to the same. The
OL,16,Fmomentum is with Reform because we are
OL,17,Fthe people's army."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1778339461
OL,3,CReform UK Leader in Wales Dan Thomas
OL,4,Cwins seat at Senedd Election
OL,6,FHe went on to add: "For decades the
OL,7,FWelsh valleys and cities such as
OL,8,FIslwyn and Newport have been ignored,
OL,9,Flet down, and forgotten by the old
OL,10,Fparties of Wales.
OL,12,F"Today the people have spoken and in
OL,13,FReform they finally have a voice. You
OL,14,Fwill not be ignored, you will not be
OL,15,Fsidelined, you will not be called
OL,16,Fnames, from now on you will be
OL,17,Frepresented by Reform."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
