PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1778339461
OL,3,CReform UK Leader in Wales Dan Thomas
OL,4,Cwins seat at Senedd Election
OL,6,FThis election is the first time in
OL,7,Fhistory Reform UK have had a candidate
OL,8,Felected into the Senedd. Laura Anne
OL,9,FJones was elected as a Conservative MS
OL,10,Fand then defected to Reform during the
OL,11,Flast Welsh Parliament term.
OL,13,FCounting is still underway in the 2026
OL,14,FSenedd Election, with all 16 of Wales'
OL,15,Fconstituencies in the process of
OL,16,Fcalculating and declaring six
OL,17,Fsuccessful candidates.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
