PN,46906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1778339461
OL,3,CReform UK Leader in Wales Dan Thomas
OL,4,Cwins seat at Senedd Election
OL,6,FThe results will be calculated using a
OL,7,Fnew voting system - the d'Hondt method
OL,8,F- which means that the results are
OL,9,Fsupposed to more proportionally
OL,10,Freflect the number of votes each party
OL,11,Freceives.
OL,13,FIt means that on polling day, people
OL,14,Fcast just one vote for the party or
OL,15,Findependent they wish to represent
OL,16,Fthem in the Senedd. Six individuals
OL,17,Fwill be elected per constituency.
OL,19,FTo get an outright majority, a party
OL,20,Fwould need at least 49 seats overall.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
